title: Moonlight Beach

review.description: My wife and I were walking west along the beach. There was a dead sea lion at the high tide line. It had been shot in the forehead! There were fresh tire marks driving by this murdered creature....
Love this beach! Great place to sit on the sand with a coffee....watching the waves break
